        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "When we use Automatic source detection we are loosing the value of $locale set in the constructor. This appends because the same $locale variable is reuse to add the translation file with ::addTranslation().\n\nSo at the end of the directory scanning when the locale is set, $locale have the value of the last added file :\n\n{code}\nif ((array_key_exists($locale, $this->_translate)) and (count($this->_translate[$locale]) > 0)) {\n    $this->setLocale($locale);\n}\n{code}\n\n\n"
        },
